data.description: Home is located right next to Miguel Ribera Park in an up & coming community close to the City and in the path of development. Most beautiful entry price point home on the market!   Check us out at a local Open House or reach out to your Real estate agent. Since the seller bought a few years ago he has made several upgrades!  Cosmetic and systems. Newer A/C unit, Heater, and Boiler.  Newer carpet and paint job,    Quality bathroom and kitchen remodel! Bathroom features a blue tooth speaker in the fan. Try it!
